	<h2>Cochi and the Challenge</h2>
	<p>
		Banregio wanted to create a web app to help young people achieve their goals and accomplish what they wanted, new generations are known for not knowing how to save money and living in the moment, spending everything without thinking in the future, but this platform was considered to help you save money for your medium term goals, either these were getting a new computer or traveling around the world.
	</p>
	<p>
		Banregio didn't want the people to relate the web app directly with them, they wanted to create something different from what they are, and to really help people accomplish things.
	</p>
	
	<h2>
		What we did
	</h2>
