	<p>
		We needed to generate and identity all of its own, it needed to be different from Banregio, so people wouldn't relate it directly to a bank and all of its tedious steps to create an account or to do any transaction.
	</p>	

	<p>
		It needed to be something not that serious but not that fun at the same time.
		They wanted it to be something obvious so we decided to explore options that reflected the name they gave us for the product "Cochi", that's how we came out with a pigs' nose for the logo, it reminded us to when we were little and wanted to save money, we had a moneybox with the shape of a pig.
	</p>
